        "title": "feat(ui/i18n): add Chinese translations for config page",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Problem: Config page quick settings had missing or incorrect Chinese translations. Theme names, roundness options, and several card labels showed raw i18n keys or English text when using Simplified Chinese locale.\n- Why it matters: Non-English users see untranslated labels in the config page appearance settings and theme selection.\n- What changed: Added zh-CN translations for config.quick theme names (爪/结/破折) and roundness options (无/轻微/默认/圆润/完全). Fixed duplicate roundness key in en.ts by introducing roundnessLabel. Fixed missing t() imports in config-form.render.ts, config-form.node.ts, and config-quick.ts. Fixed undefined SECTION_CATEGORIES in config.ts. Moved module-level t() calls in config-quick.ts to render time so locale switching works correctly.\n- What did NOT change: No functional behavior, logic, or styling changed. No other locales touched.\n\n## Change Type\n\n- [ ] Bug fix\n- [ ] Feature\n- [x] Chore/infra\n\n## Scope\n\n- [x] UI / DX\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- Behavior or issue addressed: Config page quick settings Appearance card showed raw i18n keys (config.quick.roundness.none) and English theme names (Claw/Knot/Dash) in zh-CN locale.\n- Real environment tested: Local dev gateway (port 19001).\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: Built UI with `pnpm ui:build`, started gateway, navigated to /config in Control UI with zh-CN locale active.\n- Evidence after fix: Screenshot — theme buttons display 爪/结/破折, roundness row label shows 圆角, roundness buttons display 无/轻微/默认/圆润/完全. ![Config page Chinese i18n](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/git-jxj/openclaw/f534e7352a/.github/pr-assets/config-zh-proof.png)\n- Observed result after fix: zh-CN locale shows correctly translated config quick settings UI.\n- What was not tested: Other non-English locales.\n\n## User-visible / Behavior Changes\n\n- Config page theme names now localized to Simplified Chinese.\n- Config page roundness options now localized to Simplified Chinese.\n- English locale unchanged.\n\n## Security Impact\n\n- New permissions/capabilities? (No)\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? (No)\n- New/changed network calls? (No)\n- Command/tool execution surface changed? (No)\n- Data access scope changed? (No)\n\n## Repro + Verification\n\n### Environment\n\n- OS: macOS\n- Runtime: Node 22 (local dev)\n\n### Steps\n\n1. `pnpm ui:build`\n2. `OPENCLAW_SKIP_CHANNELS=1 node scripts/run-node.mjs --dev gateway`\n3. Open Control UI, switch to zh-CN\n4. Navigate to Config page\n\n### Expected\n\n- Theme buttons: 爪, 结, 破折\n- Roundness label: 圆角\n- Roundness buttons: 无, 轻微, 默认, 圆润, 完全\n\n### Actual\n\n- All above verified locally.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- [x] Screenshot/recording\n\n![Config page Chinese i18n](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/git-jxj/openclaw/f534e7352a/.github/pr-assets/config-zh-proof.png)\n\n## Compatibility / Migration\n\n- Backward compatible? (Yes)\n- Config/env changes? (No)\n- Migration needed? (No)\n\n## Risks and Mitigations\n\nNone.",
